<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Ts2339 on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/ts2339/</link><description>Recent content in Ts2339 on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/ts2339/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] TypeScript TS2339 — Property 'X' does not exist on type 'Y'</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2339-property/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2339-property/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="ts2339--property-x-does-not-exist-on-type-y"&gt;TS2339 — Property &amp;lsquo;X&amp;rsquo; does not exist on type &amp;lsquo;Y&amp;rsquo;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TS2339 occurs when you try to access a property on a type that does not define it. TypeScript&amp;rsquo;s type system enforces that you can only access properties that exist on the declared type.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Accessing non-existent property
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;age&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;age&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;30&lt;/span&gt; };
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;email&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2339
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Wrong type annotation
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;length&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// OK
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;toFixed&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2339: string has no toFixed
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Using API response without type definition
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;response&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fetch&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;/api/user&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;response&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;json&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2339: &amp;#39;user&amp;#39; does not exist
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-add-missing-property-to-interface"&gt;Fix 1: Add missing property to interface&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;age&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;email&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-optional-chaining"&gt;Fix 2: Use optional chaining&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;email&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-type-the-api-response"&gt;Fix 3: Type the API response&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ApiResponse&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;age&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt; };
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ApiResponse&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;response&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;json&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-use-type-assertion-or-index-signature"&gt;Fix 4: Use type assertion or index signature&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;StringMap&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; [&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;key&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;map&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;StringMap&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; };
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;map&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;name&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2339-property-access/"&gt;TS2339: Property is type-only import&lt;/a&gt; — type-only import access.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2551-property/"&gt;TS2551: Property does not exist - did you mean&lt;/a&gt; — typo suggestions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2741-property/"&gt;TS2741: Property is missing in type&lt;/a&gt; — missing required property.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] TypeScript TS2339 — Property 'X' is a type-only import</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2339-property-access/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2339-property-access/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="ts2339--property-x-is-a-type-only-import"&gt;TS2339 — Property &amp;lsquo;X&amp;rsquo; is a type-only import&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TS2339 can occur when you try to use a type-only import as a value. With &lt;code&gt;verbatimModuleSyntax&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;isolatedModules&lt;/code&gt;, TypeScript enforces that type-only imports cannot be used at runtime.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Using type import as value
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;./types&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;u&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; }; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// OK as type annotation
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;u2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt;(); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2339: User is type-only
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Re-exporting type as value
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Config&lt;/span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;./config&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Config&lt;/span&gt; }; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2339: Config is type-only
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Import without &amp;#39;type&amp;#39; used as type-only
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Logger&lt;/span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;./logger&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Logger is only used as type, but imported as value
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-use-import-type-correctly"&gt;Fix 1: Use import type correctly&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;./types&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Can only use User as a type
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;u&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; };
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-separate-value-and-type-imports"&gt;Fix 2: Separate value and type imports&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;helper&lt;/span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;./utils&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Config&lt;/span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;./config&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-use-inline-type-import"&gt;Fix 3: Use inline type import&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;helper&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Config&lt;/span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;./module&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2339-property/"&gt;TS2339: Property does not exist on type&lt;/a&gt; — regular property access.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2693-x-only-referenced/"&gt;TS2693: &amp;lsquo;X&amp;rsquo; only refers to a type&lt;/a&gt; — type used as value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2307-cannot-find-module/"&gt;TS2307: Cannot find module&lt;/a&gt; — module not found.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] TypeScript TS2339 — Property Does Not Exist on Type</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2339/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2339/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="ts2339--property-x-does-not-exist-on-type-y"&gt;TS2339 — Property &amp;lsquo;X&amp;rsquo; does not exist on type &amp;lsquo;Y&amp;rsquo;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TS2339 occurs when you try to access a property on a type that doesn&amp;rsquo;t declare that property. TypeScript enforces property access based on the declared shape of types, so accessing a non-existent property is a compile-time error.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Accessing a property not in the interface
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;age&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;age&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;30&lt;/span&gt; };
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;email&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2339: Property &amp;#39;email&amp;#39; does not exist on type &amp;#39;User&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Typo in property name
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;nme&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2339: Did you mean &amp;#39;name&amp;#39;?
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Using &amp;#39;any&amp;#39; bypass but the real type is stricter
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;response&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;any&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fetch&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;/api&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;response&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;id&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Compiles with any, fails at runtime
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Accessing array methods on non-array
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;num&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;42&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;num&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;map&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2339: Property &amp;#39;map&amp;#39; does not exist on type &amp;#39;number&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="solutions"&gt;Solutions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-add-the-property-to-the-type-definition"&gt;Fix 1: Add the property to the type definition&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;age&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct — add email to the interface
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;age&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;email&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-optional-properties-or-index-signatures"&gt;Fix 2: Use optional properties or index signatures&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;age&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;email?&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Optional
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Or allow any extra properties
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;age&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; [&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;key&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;unknown&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-fix-typos-in-property-names"&gt;Fix 3: Fix typos in property names&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;nme&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-use-type-guards-before-accessing-properties"&gt;Fix 4: Use type guards before accessing properties&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;processUser&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;User&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Admin&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;email&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;email&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// OK — TypeScript knows it&amp;#39;s Admin
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: API response typed too narrowly
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ApiResponse&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;res&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ApiResponse&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; };
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;res&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;length&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2339 if data could be undefined
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Class without a property
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Animal&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;cat&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Animal&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Animal&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;cat&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sound&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;meow&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2339: Property &amp;#39;sound&amp;#39; does not exist on type &amp;#39;Animal&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2304/"&gt;TS2304: Cannot find name&lt;/a&gt; — identifier not in scope at all.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2345/"&gt;TS2345: Argument of type &amp;lsquo;X&amp;rsquo; is not assignable&lt;/a&gt; — type mismatch in function calls.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2741/"&gt;TS2741: Property is missing in type&lt;/a&gt; — missing required properties on object literal.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] TypeScript TS2339 v2 — Property Does Not Exist on Type Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2339-error-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2339-error-v2/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="ts2339--property-does-not-exist-on-type-v2"&gt;TS2339 — Property Does Not Exist on Type (v2)&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This variant of TS2339 covers situations where property access fails on union types, generic constraints, or when working with third-party library types that lack proper typings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common error messages:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;TS2339: Property 'name' does not exist on type 'User | null'&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;TS2339: Property 'data' does not exist on type 'unknown'&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;TS2339: Property 'map' does not exist on type 'T'&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;TS2339: Property 'toISOString' does not exist on type 'string | Date'&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TypeScript prevents accessing properties that the current type annotation doesn&amp;rsquo;t include. This often happens after narrowing, with union types, or when the type is inferred as &lt;code&gt;unknown&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>